      <title>苹果将​​向第三方开放支付芯片并收取费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/apple-to-open-payment-chip-to-third-parties-and-charge-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司将开始允许第三方使用 iPhone 的支付芯片来处理交易，此举将使银行和其他服务能够与 Apple Pay 平台竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/apple-to-open-payment-chip-to-third-parties-and-charge-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
