    <item>
      <title>Nubank 利润飙升推动股价上涨，抵消信贷疑虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/nubank-posts-record-revenue-profit-while-boosting-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的数字银行之一 Nu Holdings Ltd. 的第二季度利润较上年同期增长一倍以上，其股价随之上涨，掩盖了分析师对贷款拖欠率上升和不良贷款拨备下降发出的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/nubank-posts-record-revenue-profit-while-boosting-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
